metadata.name: H1 Halloween Candy
metadata.description:
Bored Mummy Halloween Royal Rumble (BMHRR) consists of 8,888 Halloween Candy. Every Genesis Bored Mummy holder can claim their candy at our member dashboard. The silent night before Halloween...

"Fate lies in your hands, it just that you need to be brave enough to see it and desire enough to change it.. here's your candy" given to you by Millennium Earl

For more info: ( https://discord.gg/boredmummywu)
